            "title": "盤中速報 - 深證成指下跌-356.11點至15763.0604點，跌幅2.21%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間02日10:27，深證成指下跌356.11點（或2.21%），暫報15763.06點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+0.42%</li><li>近 1 月：+5.08%</li><li>近 3 月：+17.6%</li><li>近 6 月：+19.18%</li><li>今年以來：+19.18%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>比亞迪概念概念領跌-8.33%。其中    TCL科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:000100:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/000100\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">000100-CN</a>)            下跌        7.03%            ;    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>中芯國際概念概念領跌-6.32%。其中    江豐電子(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:300666:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/300666\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">300666-CN</a>)            下跌        10.59%            ;        雅克科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:002409:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/002409\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">002409-CN</a>)            下跌        10%            ;        北方華創(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:002371:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/002371\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">002371-CN</a>)            下跌        9.29%    。</p></section></main>",
